# Test cities

## Sizes

The sizes represent the duration of the tests.

- 🔵 XS: runs under 5 min
- 🟢 S: runs under 15 min
- 🟡 M: runs under 60 min
- 🟠 L: runs under 180 min (1/8 day)
- 🔴 XL: runs under 360 min (1/4 day)
- 🟣 XXL: runs under 720 min (1/2 day)

